### AR (Augmented Reality) Tests
### Test AR snapshot creation and listing

@token = {{loginCustomer.response.body.accessToken}}
@productId = {{createProduct.response.body.id}}

### 1. Create AR Snapshot (User chụp ảnh với AR)
# @name createSnapshot
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/ar/snapshots
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-123",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/ar-snapshots/snapshot-1.jpg",
  "metadata": {
    "cameraPosition": {
      "x": 0,
      "y": 1.5,
      "z": 2
    },
    "lighting": "natural",
    "deviceModel": "iPhone 14 Pro"
  }
}

### 2. Create Another Snapshot
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/ar/snapshots
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-123",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/ar-snapshots/snapshot-2.jpg",
  "metadata": {
    "cameraPosition": {
      "x": 1,
      "y": 1.5,
      "z": 1.5
    },
    "lighting": "studio"
  }
}

### 3. List All AR Snapshots (Public)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/ar/snapshots?page=1&pageSize=20

### 4. List Snapshots by User
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/ar/snapshots?userId=user-123&page=1&pageSize=10

### 5. List Snapshots by Product
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/ar/snapshots?productId={{productId}}&page=1&pageSize=10

### 6. Create Anonymous Snapshot (no userId)
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/ar/snapshots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/ar-snapshots/anonymous-snapshot.jpg"
}